<h2>Chart - Styling</h2>

<p>The Chart component supports color palettes, axis configuration, and legend customization — the same styling options available in ASP.NET Web Forms.</p>

<h3>Color Palettes</h3>

<p>Use the <code>Palette</code> property to set a color scheme. Available palettes: <strong>BrightPastel</strong>, <strong>Berry</strong>, <strong>Chocolate</strong>, <strong>EarthTones</strong>, <strong>Excel</strong>, <strong>Fire</strong>, <strong>Grayscale</strong>, <strong>Light</strong>, <strong>Pastel</strong>, <strong>SeaGreen</strong>, <strong>SemiTransparent</strong>.</p>

